{"tid":543948,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打想學電結他？","createTime":"2018-01-29T04:38:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-14T19:51:32.000Z","uid":52577,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6912813dd1bceb386164b4d4c220f40bbd3bdb1b","tid":543948,"uid":52577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T04:38:15.000Z","msg":"先簡單介紹下自己先 <br />\n小弟彈左13年結他，夾左11年band，教左6年結他，持有rockschool grade 8 證書(merit)。而家都私教緊10個巴絲 。<br />\n想係度開返個電結他教學同順便收下學生吊下命（係香港做音樂真係地獄黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）。<br />\n<br />\n第一篇教學：訓練手指獨立性及速度方法<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/VNQCrSb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FVNQCrSb.jpg&h=c85fbb47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n要訓練手指獨立性及速度，多數人都會爬格仔同用唔同既pattern既scale去練，但當去到一定程度大家可能會發現左手手指到左樽頸位，點練都係再快唔到，而開始灰心。在此我教大家一個頗有效訓練手指速度，而且每日唔需要練太長時間就可以既練習，但最重要係有恆心每日keep住做。 <br />\n<br />\n呢個練習右手只需要pick每個bar第一下，之後既都係用hammering on同pulling off彈。Bar 1-3係分別用食指中指ham on pull off、食指無名指ham on pull off同埋食指尾指ham on pull off，我地用自己最快既速度去ham on 同pull off，跟住bar 4-5係中指無名指ham on pull off、中指尾指既ham on pull off。最後係無名指同尾指既ham on pull off。 <br />\n<br />\n我地最弱既通常會係食指尾指、中指無名指、中指尾指同無名指同尾指呢幾個組合，所以大家可以特別花多D時間落呢幾組度。有問題歡迎隨便發問。<br />\n<br />\n如果想揾私人1對1結他老師可以telegram揾我： <a href=\"https://t.me/royceredfield\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Froyceredfield&d=nKaxyJspJgObJ3cc5PIlbdZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=aa296d61\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/royceredfield</a>"},{"pid":"c5ef6c83f949bec7359d97d7bf15e914abf89c55","tid":543948,"uid":52577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T12:48:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7f156aed9cc273cee39a1864ab8261a2235279e","tid":543948,"uid":5557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T12:50:17.000Z","msg":"教唔教木結？"},{"pid":"d1e1f9915101b89a75daa9599684ce8439454c4b","tid":543948,"uid":52577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7f156aed9cc273cee39a1864ab8261a2235279e","tid":543948,"uid":5557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T12:50:17.000Z","msg":"教唔教木結？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T13:39:24.000Z","msg":"會，telegram傾啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0762d8954a9ee94be34582bae83906e5898bc25","tid":543948,"uid":52577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T16:27:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d092c483fb80cea2b2de7306fbd15f69ca71973","tid":543948,"uid":52577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T00:58:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9039f7966315ad55456ce913cc73c92b345b5a19","tid":543948,"uid":52577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T03:55:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc761a0009b41ee9a5f13254c052c102c807f41a","tid":543948,"uid":52577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T12:06:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4e2e1d6770cdf968e6b84603ff839b6e670b1c5","tid":543948,"uid":142964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T12:08:31.000Z","msg":"20 年前學過一年，而家完全唔記得晒，但有電結他....都唔知壞左未，而家想學返，巴打收幾銀一堂先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84c4bb76ae64e08d893d3537e8460a56e70e8263","tid":543948,"uid":52577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4e2e1d6770cdf968e6b84603ff839b6e670b1c5","tid":543948,"uid":142964,"like":0,